detail_desc: Cotton corduroy trousers with wide stripes, a regular waist and zip fly with a concealed hook-and-eye fastener. Side pockets, welt back pockets and slightly shorter straight legs.
Cardigan in soft, fluffy faux fur with long sleeves and no fasteners. Jersey lining.

Nylon jacket with a filling of 80% down and 20% feathers. Detachable, lined hood with a faux fur trim, a fleece-lined stand-up collar and a zip and wind flap with press-studs down the front and a chin guard at the top. Patch front pockets with a flap, and concealed elastication at the cuffs. Partly lined in fleece.
Jumper in soft, fine-knit cotton with appliqués at the top, a ribbed stand-up collar with a zip, and ribbing at the cuffs and hem.
Fabric bag with a print motif on the front and two handles at the top. Size 34x40 cm.
Jumper in soft, fine-knit cashmere with wide ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem and sewn-in turn-ups at the cuffs.
One-shoulder, ankle-length jumpsuit with elastication and a wide flounce at the top, elasticated seam at the waist and straight, wide legs. Unlined.
5-pocket jeans in washed stretch denim with a regular waist, button fly and skinny legs.
Cap with a motif, covered button on top and an adjustable plastic fastener at the back.
Short, straight-cut T-shirt dress in sturdy cotton jersey with a round, rib-trimmed neckline. Unlined.
Short, sleeveless V-neck dress in a cotton weave with broderie anglaise. Narrow, frilled shoulder straps, a concealed zip and a tie at the back and a seam at the waist. Lined.

Baby Exclusive. Sleeveless romper suit in soft, organic cotton jersey with buttons at the top. Side pockets, 3/4-length legs with sewn-in turn-ups, and concealed press-studs at the crotch and down the legs.
Fabric-covered Alice band with a decorative knot detail.
Metal hair clip with bead appliqués in various designs. Length 8 cm.
Wide, V-neck jumper in a soft, fine knit with dropped shoulders, long sleeves and ribbing at the cuffs and hem.
Baby Exclusive. T-shirts in soft, organic cotton jersey with a concealed press-stud on one shoulder.
Chelsea boots with elastic gores in the sides and a loop at the back. Fabric linings and insoles. Heel 2.5 cm.
Sleeveless top with a V-neck front and back.
Straight-cut off-the-shoulder blouse in a crinkled weave with narrow elastication and a wide flounce at the top. Long sleeves with flounced cuffs.
Long cardigan in a soft, fine knit with long sleeves and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. No buttons.
Long-sleeved bodysuits in soft organic cotton jersey with press-studs on one shoulder and at the crotch.
Cotton jersey vest tops with ribbing around the neckline and armholes.
Calf-length circular skirt in woven fabric with a high waist and a concealed button and zip at one side. Unlined.
5-pocket, ankle-length jeans in washed, slightly stretch denim made partly from recycled cotton with a high waist, zip fly and button and gently tapered legs.
Shirt in checked flannel with a collar and chest pocket. Regular fit.

Ankle-length suit trousers in a linen and cotton weave with a concealed hook-and-eye fastening and zip fly. Side pockets, jetted back pockets with a button and legs with creases and sewn-in turn-ups at the hems. Slim Fit – a fit that is close-fitting at the thighs, knees and ankles to create a fitted silhouette.

Tunic in a patterned viscose weave with a collar, buttons at the top and an open chest pocket. Long sleeves with narrow elastication at the cuffs, a gathered seam at the waist and a gently rounded hem. Slightly longer at the back. Unlined.
Double-layered hat in a soft, fine knit containing glittery threads with embroidery on the turned-up hem and faux fur pompoms on top.
Calf-length dress in softly draping viscose jersey with a V-neck front and back, elastication over the shoulders and short, wide sleeves. Seam under the bust and a flared skirt. Unlined.
Boxer briefs in soft cotton jersey with an elasticated waist and a decorative bow at the front. Lined gusset.
Short nightdress in soft jersey with a lace-trimmed V-neck and narrow, adjustable shoulder straps.

Thigh boots in imitation suede with a soft, stretchy shaft, rounded toes and block heels. Jersey linings and insoles and fluted soles. The polyester content of the boots is partly recycled. Height of soles 1 cm. Heel 6.5 cm.
V-neck top in softly draping viscose jersey. Smocked, frill-trimmed yoke at the shoulders, flutter sleeves and a narrow, elasticated seam under the bust.
Baby Exclusive. Jumper in soft, rib-knit merino wool with ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.

Single-breasted jacket in a stretch weave with narrow notch lapels with a decorative buttonhole, a chest pocket, flap front pockets and one inner pocket. Two buttons at the front, decorative buttons at the cuffs and a single back vent. Lined. Slim fit that tapers at the chest and waist which, combined with slightly narrower sleeves, creates a fitted silhouette.
Long-sleeved body in lace with a V-neck, mesh side sections and press-studs at the crotch. Lined bust.
Fancy dress costume in soft velour. Hood with embroidered details and appliqués, and ribbing at the cuffs and hems.
Relaxed-fit shorts in a cotton weave with an elasticated drawstring waist, fake fly, side pockets, a welt back pocket and short, wide legs.
Sturdy, round, imitation leather shoulder bag with a quilted front. Zip at the top, one small inner compartment and a metal chain shoulder strap. Lined. Size 5x18.5 cm.
Imitation leather hi-tops with lacing at the front and a loop at the back. Mesh linings and insoles and chunky, patterned soles.

Padded all-in-one suit in windproof, breathable functional fabric with closed, waterproof seams and a detachable lined hood with a detachable faux fur trim. Zip down the front with a chin guard, zipped side pockets, and elastication at the cuffs, hems and back of the waist. Reinforced back and legs, and a reinforced elastic strap under the feet. Reflective details. The suit has a water-repellent coating without fluorocarbons.
3/4-length trousers in jersey with covered elastication at the waist, a decorative bow at the front and wide, straight legs.
Plastic hair claws. Height 2.5 cm, width 35 cm.
Suede ankle boots with peep toes and a frayed-end drawstring on the shaft. Leather linings and insoles and rubber soles. Heel 8.5 cm.
T-shirts in soft cotton jersey with a print motif and gently rounded hem.
Shorts in washed cotton twill with an adjustable elasticated waist, zip fly and button, side pockets and fake welt back pockets with a button.

Fitted jacket in fast-drying functional fabric designed to help keep you dry and cool while exercising. Hood, zip down the front with a chin guard and zipped front pockets for safe storage of valuables. Extra-long sleeves with thumbholes to help keep you warm while exercising outside. The sleeves are in a raglan cut to minimise the risk of friction from the seams.
Wide, straight-cut T-shirt in cotton jersey with a yoke front and back, short sleeves with print stripes and a rounded hem. Slightly longer at the back.
Fitted skirt in sturdy stretch jersey with an elasticated waist. Slightly shorter at the front. Unlined.

Warm-lined boots in waterproof functional fabric with imitation leather details and a padded, ankle-length shaft with a faux fur trim. Adjustable elasticated lacing at the front, a zip in the side and reflective details. Pile linings and insoles and rubber soles.

Waterproof hi-tops in mesh and imitation leather with a padded edge and tongue. Hook and loop tab at the top, elasticated lacing at the front and a loop at the back. Mesh linings and insoles and rubber soles.
Ribbed T-shirt in stretch cotton jersey.
Top in soft, patterned viscose jersey with an opening at the top and narrow ties at the neckline. Short, flounced sleeves with smocking over the shoulders, and gathers in the side seams for best fit.
Blouse in woven fabric with a slight sheen. Small, gathered stand-up collar, a V-neck opening and concealed buttons at the front and short, wide, raglan sleeves with ties.
Top in slub cotton jersey with an interactive appliqué on the front, short cap sleeves, narrow ribbing around the neckline and short slits at the sides.
Short, off-the-shoulder top in ribbed jersey with overlocked edges, a concealed silicone trim at the top and long sleeves.
Temporary face tattoos in various sizes, 13 of which are glow-in-the-dark.

Set with a jumper and pair of trousers in jacquard-knit cotton. Jumper with a round, ribbed neckline, buttons on one shoulder, long sleeves and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Trousers with a drawstring waist and ribbed hems.
Blouse in an airy weave with pleats at the shoulders and a wrapover front with a concealed press-stud. Short, wide sleeves and smocking at the back of the hem.
Boxer shorts in a cotton weave with an elasticated waist, long legs and button fly.
Straight-cut top in a softly draping weave with a concealed zip at the back, dropped shoulders and short sleeves in a double layer of flounces.
Fitted top in stretch jersey with a round neck and long sleeves.
Microfibre thong briefs with a low waist, lined gusset, narrow sides and string back.
Double-layered hat in a soft rib knit with a sewn-in turn-up at the hem with a small fabric appliqué on the front.
Short, 5-pocket shorts in washed stretch denim with worn details, a regular waist, zip fly and raw-edge hems.

Shirt in a linen and cotton weave with a concealed button-down collar, classic front and open chest pocket. Long sleeves with adjustable buttoning at the cuffs, a yoke with a pleat at the back, and a rounded hem. Slim Fit – a fit with narrow shoulders and a tapered waist for a fitted silhouette.
Long, straight-cut jacket in woven fabric with notch lapels, a fastening with one button at the front and patch front pockets. Lined.
Short, bell-shaped skirt in sturdy jersey with a slight sheen and elastication at the waist. Unlined.
Clutch bag with a detachable metal chain shoulder strap, open inner compartment and flap with a decorative metal buckle and concealed magnetic fastener. Lined. Depth 5 cm. Height 15 cm. Length 20 cm.
Shorts in a cotton weave with an elasticated drawstring waist.
Jacquard-knit socks in various colours and designs.
Short, sleeveless dress in sturdy jersey with a low-cut back, seam at the waist and flared skirt. The polyester content of the dress is partly recycled.
Soft nursing tops in organic cotton jersey with shaped cups and narrow adjustable shoulder straps. Soft integral top with a functional fastening for easier nursing access and an elasticated hem.
Ankle-length jeans in washed stretch denim with a regular waist, fake front pockets, real back pockets and skinny legs.
Cropped top in smocked cotton jersey with elastication at the top and overlocked edges at the top and bottom.

Lightweight cotton flannel shirt in a straight, gently tapered fit with a button-down collar, classic front and open chest pocket. Yoke with a pleat at the back, long sleeves with adjustable buttoning at the cuffs, and a rounded hem.
Vest tops in soft organic cotton jersey.
Top in soft sweatshirt fabric with long raglan sleeves, a motif on the front and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.

Playsuit in woven fabric with broderie anglaise. V-neck and buttons at the top, an opening and concealed button at the back of the neck and short, raglan sleeves with a frill trim. Elasticated seam and a detachable tie belt at the waist, side pockets and short, wide legs. Lined lower section.
Short-sleeved jumper in soft, fine-knit cashmere with ribbing around the neckline, sleeves and hem.
